STATE
v.
Tamica Yvette MIMS. No. 5P07. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 3, 2007. John C. Evans, Assistant Attorney General, Michael Nifong, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 22nd day of January 2007 by Defendant to Withdraw Notice of *537Appeal and Petition for Discretionary Review:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference this the 3rd day of May 2007."
